&lt;p&gt;簡單&lt;a href="https://nfuedu-my.sharepoint.com/:v:/g/personal/yen_nfu_edu_tw/EQgJcYlnkwJHgDlwwlGQ46YBp8v8l3GSyur9ylIompMArg?nav=eyJyZWZlcnJhbEluZm8iOnsicmVmZXJyYWxBcHAiOiJPbmVEcml2ZUZvckJ1c2luZXNzIiwicmVmZXJyYWxBcHBQbGF0Zm9ybSI6IldlYiIsInJlZmVycmFsTW9kZSI6InZpZXciLCJyZWZlcnJhbFZpZXciOiJNeUZpbGVzTGlua0NvcHkifX0&amp;amp;e=WLHbf6"&gt;說明&lt;/a&gt;如何利用 Gmail 帳號登入 &lt;a href="https://chat.openai.com/auth/login"&gt;chatgpt&lt;/a&gt;, 並進行提問.&lt;/p&gt;
